So here's how to fix this issue (maybe--it worked for my very simple test). Add the following code at line 47

```
    def patch_xml(self,src_xml):
        #remove all “curly” quotes (single and double) found within {% %} and replace with straight
        def stripquotes(m):
            return re.sub(r'[“”‘’]+','\"',m.group(0),flags=re.DOTALL)
        src_xml = re.sub(r'(?<=\{\%).*?(?=\%\})',stripquotes,src_xml,flags=re.DOTALL)
```

I'm interested in hearing whether that works for anybody else.

