@tqchen , @piiswrong , I am making using of MXNet 0.12.0 version. When I am saving the symbol file in JSON format, I get the output in this format for various types of layers:

```
      {
      "op": "Convolution", 
      "name": "convolution5", 
      "attr": {
        "kernel": "(3, 3)", 
        "num_filter": "16", 
        "stride": "(1, 1)"
      }, 
      "inputs": [[6, 0, 0], [7, 0, 0], [8, 0, 0]]
    }, 
    {
      "op": "Activation", 
