@thet  you're right ... if they aren't define, they aren't reset. So the reset-script needs fallback:

    define = _old_define !== 'undefined' ? _old_define : undefined;
    require = _old_require !== 'undefined' ? _old_require : undefined;

this should do the trick ...

@samuell You made your rowStartPosition way too small, you want

    return rowStartPosition(depth-1)+Math.max(Math.min(rowSizes[depth-1], 100)*10+10,100);

to get enough room between rows by limit it to the 100 your modulus gives you.

